snippet.title: Chivalry 2 - Regicide Trailer
snippet.description:
OUT 5/22 - REGICIDE IS HERE! 👑

Chivalry 2’s Regicide Update introduces the epic Team Objective Map – Regicide at Trayan Citadel, the new Goedendag weapon, a new Campaign, quality of life improvements, and more!

Chivalry 2 is available now with Cross-Play on Steam, Epic Games Store, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, PlayStation 4 & PlayStation 5. 

Discord: http://discord.gg/chivalry2
Twitter: http://twitter.com/chivalrygame
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Chivalry2
Website: http://chivalry2.com

Torn Banner Studios
